synergyText: RegularDamage=(Level200×130×ATKDDEF)×Modifier

Damage can be blocked if the target who would have taken damage has the Evading Condition or the Electric Synthesize Trait.

name: Winter Call
description: A wintry sonata that leaves all Temtem in the battlefield as Frozen as the Kilima snows while gifting the user with ATK .
effectText: Winter Call inflicts all other Temtem on the battlefield with the Frozen Condition for 2 turns while gifting the user with ATK .
